    01: Physical Control                       0x003d
          RGMII Receive Timing Control         Default
          RGMII Transmit Timing Control        Default
          200 BASE Mode                        100
          Flow Control's Forced value          0
          Force Flow Control                   0
          Link's Forced value                  Up
          Force Link                           1
